OL,5, Women will soon be allowed to swim     
OL,6, topless in Berlin's public pools, after
OL,7, a ruling by the city's authorities.    
OL,9,FIt comes after a woman who was thrown  
OL,10,Fout of an open-air pool for sunbathing 
OL,11,Ftopless took legal action.             
OL,13,FA second woman said she was told to    
OL,14,Fcover up while at an indoor pool in    
OL,15,FDecember.                              
OL,17,FAuthorities agreed they had been       
OL,18,Fvictims of discrimination and said that
OL,19,Fall visitors to Berlin's pools were now
OL,20,Fentitled to go topless.                
